## ЁЯУМ What Is This File?

`Company.java` represents a **registered company** on the SolveStack platform. A Company is a special type of User whose primary purpose is to **post innovation challenges** and **review solutions** submitted by Developers.

This class extends `User`, which means it inherits all authentication and profile management capabilities, and adds its own layer of challenge management on top.

---

## ЁЯОп Purpose & Responsibility

| Responsibility | How It Is Handled |
|---|---|
| Represent a company identity | Fields: `companyName`, `industry`, `registrationNumber` |
| Post new challenges | `createChallenge(...)` method |
| Modify existing challenges | `editChallenge(...)` method |
| Remove active challenges | `closeChallenge(String challengeId)` |
| Review incoming submissions | `viewSubmissions(String challengeId)` |
| Update challenge deadlines | `updateChallengeDeadline(...)` method |
| Track total submissions | `totalSubmissionsReceived` counter |

