## ЁЯПЧ How Company Fits in the Architecture

```
User (abstract)
 тФФтФАтФА Company
       тФВ
       тФЬтФАтФА creates тФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтЦ║ Challenge
       тФВ                           тФВ
       тФВ                           тФФтФАтФА contains тФАтФАтЦ║ List<Submission>
       тФВ
       тФФтФАтФА reviewed by тФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтЦ║ Admin (via setVerified / setBanned)
```

A `Company` owns its `Challenge` objects. Each `Challenge` holds a list of `Submission` objects created by `Developer` users. The `Evaluator` scores those submissions. The `Admin` governs whether a Company is allowed to operate on the platform.

